PN,40401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FMount Batten beach in Plymouth has
OL,7,Fbeen shut until further notice after
OL,8,Fmaterial containing hazardously high
OL,9,Flevels of asbestos fibres was found in
OL,10,Fthe sand.
OL,12,FThe director of the UK Health Security
OL,13,FAgency made the decision on the
OL,14,Fmorning of Friday 10 July to protect
OL,15,Fthe public. The authority says levels
OL,16,Fare "concerning" and would pose a risk
OL,17,Fto health if inhaled.
OL,19,FFurther investigations and tests now
OL,20,Fneed to be carried out.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
