FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FAsbestos was previously used in
OL,7,Fbuilding construction and is only
OL,8,Fhazardous to health if it breaks down
OL,9,Fand fibres are released into the air.
OL,11,FMaterial containing asbestos was first
OL,12,Fidentified on the beach in 2019. At
OL,13,Fthe time, a very low level of asbestos
OL,14,Ffibres was found in just one of 16
OL,15,Fsand samples.
OL,17,FPlymouth City Council says the beach
OL,18,Fwas safe enough to stay open, as long
OL,19,Fas signage remained in place to warn
OL,20,Fbeachgoers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FIt collected 500kg of asbestos-
OL,7,Fcontaining material from the beach in
OL,8,F2019, and has continued to collect
OL,9,Fmaterial from the beach every two
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FIt says the majority of the material
OL,13,Fhas been small pebbles or rocks that
OL,14,Fcontain asbestos, washed up by the
OL,15,Ftide.
OL,17,FLevels now deemed "hazardous waste"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FThe council says recent reviews of the
OL,7,Frisk assessments have shown that since
OL,8,F2019, the volume of asbestos material
OL,9,Fbeing collected from the beach has not
OL,10,Freduced over time.
OL,12,FIt added: "A dive survey was
OL,13,Finconclusive in finding the source for
OL,14,Fthe material. Repeat sampling of the
OL,15,Fsand in recent weeks has found
OL,16,Fasbestos fibres in 14 of 16 sand
OL,17,Fsamples, with two asbestos types
OL,18,Fpresent and at levels deemed
OL,19,F'hazardous waste' by the contractor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,F"These fibres represent a risk to
OL,7,Fhealth if inhaled."
OL,9,FProfessor Steve Maddern, Plymouth
OL,10,FDirector of Public Health, added:
OL,11,F"Closing a beach that is well used by
OL,12,Flocal residents is the last thing we
OL,13,Fwant to do and we understand the
OL,14,Fdisappointment this will cause but the
OL,15,Flatest sand samples are concerning and
OL,16,Fwe must prioritise the safety of the
OL,17,Fpublic.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,F"We need to carry out further tests,
OL,7,Fincluding assessing the risk of
OL,8,Fairborne fibres and conducting a
OL,9,Ffurther survey to try and trace
OL,10,Fexactly where the materials are coming
OL,11,Ffrom.
OL,13,F"I would urge everyone, for their own
OL,14,Fsafety, to take notice of the signage
OL,15,Faround the beach and not to enter
OL,16,Fareas that have been closed. Once we
OL,17,Fhave carried out further tests, we
OL,18,Fwill know what needs to be done to
OL,19,Freduce the risks on the beach.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,F"We would ask everyone to bear with us
OL,7,Fand be patient while this work takes
OL,8,Fplace and to enjoy the other beautiful
OL,9,Fareas of the Mount Batten peninsula,
OL,10,Fincluding the Mount Batten Watersports
OL,11,Fand Activities Centre, in the
OL,12,Fmeantime."
OL,14,F"Catastrophic for our business"
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FMany business owners in the area have
OL,7,Fexpressed their concerns. June Liew,
OL,8,Fowner of Galley Kitchen, told ITV
OL,9,FNews: "We've had this before in 2019
OL,10,Fand it was a devastating effect for
OL,11,Feveryone involved and took such a long
OL,12,Ftime to get sorted.
OL,14,F"It was catastrophic for our business
OL,15,F- we had no summer trade at all".
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Dr Teresa Cullip,
OL,18,FConsultant in Public Health at
OL,19,FPlymouth City Council, said the
OL,20,Fcouncil are planning further testing
OL,21,Fof the beach next week.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,F"In the following weeks, we're doing a
OL,7,Ffull review of the whole peninsula, to
OL,8,Fmake sure we haven't missed anything.
OL,9,FIt may be a prolonged period that the
OL,10,Fbeach is shut for".
OL,12,FWhat should I do if I've been to the
OL,13,Fbeach and am worried?
OL,15,FThe council says current evidence does
OL,16,Fnot indicate any immediate risk to
OL,17,Fpeople who have recently visited the
OL,18,Fbeach, and the presence of asbestos
OL,19,Ffibres on an open beach should not
OL,20,Fresult in any breathing difficulties
OL,21,For other immediate symptoms.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783929040
OL,3,CPlymouth beach shut after hazardously
OL,4,Chigh levels of asbestos fibres found
OL,6,FIt's closing the beach to conduct
OL,7,Fwider sampling of the sand and to
OL,8,Fcarry out air disturbance testing-
OL,9,F which will help to establish the
OL,10,Fextent of the health risk.
OL,12,FAnyone with health concerns should
OL,13,Fseek advice from their GP or contact
OL,14,FNHS 111.
OL,16,FMore information can be found on the
OL,17,Fcouncil's website. It says it will be
OL,18,Fkeeping residents and businesses
OL,19,Fupdated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
